item.title: Interesting things I saw this week - 29
item.description: I’ve spent most of my free time painting, and probably will keep it like that until #linktober ends, so all my posts through this month will most likely be very short. Here are my entries this last week. Day 11: Ganon/Ganondorf. Ganondorf playing the pipe organ. Ocarina of Time. Day 12: Mask. Zant’s Helmet. Twilight Princess. Day 13: Sheikah. Impa. Skyward Sword. Day 14: Food. A bowl of Yeto’s superb soup.

item.title: Interesting things I saw this week - 28
item.description: This week I was inspired by this artist and decided to try my hand at this year’s #linktober, the goal is to make a zelda related art piece a day through the month of october, I decided to make paintings in my DSi because that’s what I have and I thought it could be fun to do something artistic even when I’m not the artistic type.
